'''''Have You Seen Drum Recently?''''' yasohotse 1989, ni film ikaba ikoresha amafoto aturuka muri ''Drum'' archives ikaba ivuga inkuru kinyamakuru n'inyandiko  ku buzima bw'umuco na politiki ya [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] .

Mu myaka ya za 1950, ''Ingoma'' yibanze ku birabura bo mu mijyi baba mu isi yiganjemo ivanguramoko. Harimo ingingo zerekeye umujyi wa jazz umujyi w'ubugizi bwa nabi, ibihimbano na siporo byerekanaga ibyiringiro, ibyifuzo no kwiheba byumujyi, umujyi wigishije abirabura 

Iyobowe na Jürgen Schadeberg, iyi filime ikubiyemo amashusho ya Oliver Tambo nk'umunyamategeko, Trevor Huddleston yerekanye ko yamaganye isenywa rya Sophiatown, Nelson Mandela wagaragaye mu bakinnyi bateramakofe, Chief Luthuli wegukanye igihembo cyitiriwe Nobel ndetse n'umuririmbyi Miriam Makeba .

Umuziki winyuma ushingiye kumuziki wo muri 1950, harimo itsinda rinini, jazz, swing, kwela na [[:en:Tin_whistle|penny whistle]].
